{"route":{"route":"/posts/d22ffdb6/","outputPath":"posts/d22ffdb6/index.html","kind":"post","title":"让win10的UWP应用走代理","language":"zh-Hans","params":{"abbrlink":"d22ffdb6"}},"description":"原因 因为uwp应用的特殊性,即使使用proxifier和proxycap这种应用也无法让其走代理 现在可直接用WindowsLoopbackManager WindowsLoopbackManager 1.SSTAP 这个应用是创建虚拟网卡,让windows全局走代理.但其有弊端就是有一些国内的网站也会走代理,比如B","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/让win10的UWP应用走代理.md","route":"/posts/d22ffdb6/","abbrlink":"d22ffdb6","title":"让win10的UWP应用走代理","date":"2018-02-08 15:09:16","updated":"2020-03-01 15:09:16","tags":["Proxy"],"categories":["Network"],"language":"zh-Hans","htmlLang":"zh-Hans","locale":"zh_CN","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"zh-CN","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<h2 id=\"原因\">原因</h2>\n<p>因为uwp应用的特殊性,即使使用proxifier和proxycap这种应用也无法让其走代理</p>\n<h2 id=\"现在可直接用windowsloopbackmanager\">现在可直接用WindowsLoopbackManager</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/tiagonmas/Windows-Loopback-Exemption-Manager\">WindowsLoopbackManager</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"1sstap\">1.SSTAP</h2>\n<p>这个应用是创建虚拟网卡,让windows全局走代理.但其有弊端就是有一些国内的网站也会走代理,比如BILIBILI.虽然可以自己写规则但实在是麻烦无比.</p>\n<h2 id=\"2fiddler\">2.fiddler</h2>\n<p>利用fiddler的winconfig实现uwp应用走代理<br>\n<img src=\"http://blog-1254450445.cossgp.myqcloud.com/WK%290~%29WR%29N79$KZ4HZZTDQ2.png\" alt=\".\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><br>\n把要走代理的应用勾上<br>\n<img src=\"http://blog-1254450445.cossgp.myqcloud.com/KT3%28H@%60C63P@2KH_X7C@QDI.png\" alt=\".\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><br>\n但这不是全局代理,只能让uwp应用走代理</p>\n","rawMarkdown":"","plainText":"","toc":[{"id":"原因","text":"原因","level":2},{"id":"现在可直接用windowsloopbackmanager","text":"现在可直接用WindowsLoopbackManager","level":2},{"id":"1sstap","text":"1.SSTAP","level":2},{"id":"2fiddler","text":"2.fiddler","level":2}],"slugForSearch":"d22ffdb6","comments":true,"math":false,"mermaid":false}}